# COLIBRÍ Blocks
#
# This file defines the blocks that are loaded or unloaded.
#
# Empty lines and lines beginning with # are ignored.
#
# The first four fields are:
#
# 1. Action. Either "load" or "unload".
#
# 2. Priority. A letter possibly followed by a number. The letter indicates the 
# primary prority, with a being highest priority and z being lowest
# priority. The number indicates the secondary priority, with 0 being higher priority 
# and 9 belong lowest priority.
#
# 3. Duplicates. The number of copies of the block file that are loaded into the
# queue. This is useful when breaking long observations into shorter blocks;
# simply set this field to the number times you want to run the shorter block.
#
# 4. Block file. This can be a file name or a shell glob pattern to match a set
# of file names. Omit the trailing ".json".
#
# After the first four columns, it is possible to add a time specification:
#
# - day M N. Carry out the action every N days. Specifically, only load
# the block files into the queue if M = D mod N, in which D is the day of the
# year (1 to 366).
#
# - date YYYMMDD. Carry out the action on the specified UTC date.
#
# If no time specification is given, the action is carried out every day.

load a0 1 0004-initial-focus-*
load b0 1 0004-focus-*

#load d4 2 3001-ngc-6334-v
load d5 3 3001-1es-1959+65-tequila

# Normal GO blocks run at priority e.

# load e1 1 2009-mera
load   e2 1 2010-globus-*
load   e3 1 2011-watson-*
load   e4 1 2001-ibarra-*      day 0 3
load   e5 1 2005-globus-*
load   e6 1 2012-watson-*
load   e7 1 2013-watson-*
load   e8 1 2007-pereyra-*     day 0 2

# Polarimetric standards
load k1 1 0021-standard-unpolarized-*0
load k1 1 0022-standard-polarized-*0

# Run the photometric monitor at medium priority once per week
load k1 1 0005-photometric-monitor-* day 0 7

# Run the biases and darks at medium priority
load k2 1 0002-biases-1
load k3 3 0003-darks-1

load z0 1 0002-biases-1
load z1 3 0003-darks-1
load z2 1 0002-biases-1
load z3 3 0003-darks-1
load z4 1 0001-twilight-flats-evening-tequila-0
load z5 1 0001-twilight-flats-evening-ddrago-0
load z9 1 0003-darks-morning-0

include BLOCKS-targets
